messages.message: <!here> hello, i notice that there are only 27 people in the <#C029Z1XRKGR|> channel, but we definitely have more than 27 engineers at Instabase! :slightly_smiling_face: Unless you never submit a PR, you should join the golden test channel, and actively monitoring the next test run / the next dogfood push after you merge a PR to make sure that you didn’t break anything unexpectedly (or confirm that if anything breaks, it’s not your PR). Please join, thanks all!
